sleep-timer CHANGELOG
=====================

v1.0.0 (2026-03-05)
--------------------
Initial release.

Features:
- Per-player sleep timers with configurable duration (1–480 minutes)
- Preset durations: 15, 30, 45, 60, 90 minutes + custom
- Smooth volume fade-out before stopping/pausing (configurable 0–120 seconds)
- Volume restore after timer expiry
- SDUI dashboard with 3 tabs: Timer, Settings, About
- Live countdown with progress bar and status badges
- JSON-RPC commands: sleeptimer.set, sleeptimer.status, sleeptimer.cancel
- Jive menu integration for Squeezebox hardware players
- Timer history with configurable max entries
- Event integration: auto-cancel on player disconnect
- Multi-player support: independent timers per player
- Extend active timers by +15 minutes
